<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">

    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1a1a1a;">{{ title }}</h2>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #888; font-size: 13px;">{{ date }}</p>

    {% if summary %}
    <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #555; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">{{ summary }}</p>
    {% endif %}

    {% if tags | length > 0 %}
    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
      {% for tag in tags %}
      <span style="display: inline-block; background: #eef2ff; color: #4a6cf7; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 4px 4px 0;">{{ tag }}</span>
      {% endfor %}
    </p>
    {% endif %}

    <div style="color: #333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      {{ body }}
    </div>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8; margin-bottom: 16px;">

    <p style="margin: 0; color: #aaa; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.8;">
      此邮件由太极量化系统自动发送。
      <br>
      如不想再收到每日报告，请<a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}" style="color: #2b6cb0;">点击这里退订</a>。
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
